title: Modi govt to give preference to 'Agniveers'; Mulls opening ONGC top post for military officers
description: Hindustan Times has learnt that the government is planning to open the top post in Oil & Natural Gas Corporation (ONGC) for military officers. Sources told HT that the government is considering formally opening chief executive positions in its blue-chip companies to senior armed force officers in ONGC. They added government is considering formally opening chief executive positions in its blue-chip companies to senior armed force officers. Remember, the top post in ONGC has been vacant since April 1, 2021. As per HT report, companies controlled by the central government may soon be asked to give preference to Agniveers, soldiers recruited under the new Agnipath scheme, on merit in various junior-level positions after they complete their tour of duty. Watch this video for more details.|#agnipath #agniveer #modigovernment #india #ongc #agnipath #agnipathprotest #military #armedforces #defenceforces

title: AHY: Saya dan Bapak Surya Paloh Sepakat untuk Lebih Kuat dan Terbuka
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Selain Partai Demokrasi Indonesia Perjuangan magnet baru dalam peta politik Indonesia saat ini, adalah Partai Nasdem.||||Nasdem didatangi para pimpinan partai yang bicara koalisi dalam Pemilu 2024.||||Setelah pimpinan Partai Keadilan Sejahtera atau PKS, pada Rabu 22 Juni 2022, maka ada empat ketua umum partai yang sudah bertemu Ketua Umum Surya Paloh di kantornya, Nasdem Tower.||||Elite PKS dipimpin Presidennya Ahmad Syaikhu bertemu pimpinan Nasdem yang dipimpin Surya Paloh.||||Namun dalam pertemuan selama dua jam, Surya dan Syaikhu belum menyepakati koalisi.||||Nasdem dan PKS baru sepakat menyiapkan kerja sama politik dalam Pemilu serentak 2024.||||Hal tersebut juga disepakati oleh Agus Harimurti Yudhoyono yang merupakan ketua umum Partai Demokrat.||||Usai melaksanakan pertemuan tertutup tersebut, Surya Paloh dan AHY mengungkapkan bahwa kunjungan tersebut mengeratkan hubungan Partai NasDem dan Partai Demokrat. ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/302087/ahy-saya-dan-bapak-surya-paloh-sepakat-untuk-lebih-kuat-dan-terbuka

title: Pyar Tune Kya Kiya | Hindi Full Movie | Fardeen Khan | Urmila Matondkar | Sonali Kulkarni
description: Pyar Tune Kya Kiya | Hindi Full Movie | Fardeen Khan | Urmila Matondkar | Sonali Kulkarni|Directed by- Rajat Mukherjee|Written by- Rajat Mukherjee|Produced by Ram Gopal Varma|Starring -Urmila Matondkar, Fardeen Khan, Sonali Kulkarni|Cinematography- Sanjay Kapoor|Edited by -Chandan Arora|Music by -Sandeep Chowta|Synopsis:-|Ria (Urmila Matondkar) is a headstrong loner angry woman and the only daughter of a rich businessman in Mumbai, Mr Jaiswal (Suresh Oberoi). Jaiswal loves his daughter but is concerned about her possessive nature. One day Ria sets out for a vacation in Goa. Jai (Fardeen Khan) is a fashion photographer, happily married to Geeta (Sonali Kulkarni). He meets Ria and takes photos of her without permission and publishes them in the magazine he works for. The magazine becomes a hit because of the pictures. The chief editor wants Ria to model for their magazine but she refuses because she is angry at Jai for publishing her pictures without asking her. Jai manages to convince her to model and she falls in love with him. She wants to talk to Jai about marriage but when she visits his home, she is shocked to meet Geeta. Shaken and distraught, Ria slips into depression.|Ria confesses her feelings to Jai, who is startled. Seeing her weeping so much, he tells her that he would have accepted her love if not married. Jai tells Geeta everything and vows to stay away from Ria. However, Ria starts to get possessive about Jai, unable to forget him. She makes a suicide attempt and calls him in the middle of the night. Jai has no choice but to save and console her. This troubles Geeta and she tells Jai to file a police complaint. Jai and Geeta mend their relationship and go out on a date but that same night, Ria breaks down and Jai consoles her again. This angers Geeta even more.|Jai attends a company party with Geeta, not knowing that Ria has also been invited. Ria now wants Jai at any cost and flirts with him in front of Geeta, who leaves fuming. At home, Jai and Geeta have a huge argument and Geeta leaves in anger. She realizes her mistake and decides to go back but Ria breaks in and starts getting intimate with Jai. Geeta enters the house and loses control on seeing them. She accidentally falls onto a glass table and hurts her head. Jai takes her to the hospital.|Ria tells Geeta that she should leave the marriage and let her and Jai live happily. Geeta explains that Jai does not love Ria as she so thinks and nothing can break their relationship. Jai decides to leave the city because of Ria's obsessive nature. Ria calls, asking to meet one last time. Jai agrees but instead goes to meet Mr Jaiswal and tells him the truth. Jai calls Geeta and hears her being attacked by someone.|It's Ria, who has become completely unstable. She attempts to kill Geeta so that she can win Jai's love. Geeta tries to escape but fails. Just as Ria is about to kill her, Jai arrives. He pleads with her to let Geeta go and he will leave Geeta to be with her. Ria, convinced, runs toward Jai but he slaps her hard, making her unconscious. Mr Jaiswal arrives and Jai tells him what Ria did.|Six months later, Geeta and Jai are happy with their life once again while Ria is housed at a mental hospital. Her father arrives at Jai's house, asking him to meet her one last time as it's her birthday and it's only Jai that can make any impact on her. Jai agrees. Upon seeing Jai, Ria loses control and shakes him until her father and the hospital crew pull her away. Jai is left feeling guilty at Ria's mental condition.|For More Updates, Subscribe to;|For Blockbuster Movies|https://www.youtube.com/user/VenusMovies|For Movies in Regional Languages: |https://www.youtube.com/venusmoviesregional|Also You Can:|'LIKE' us on Facebook: |https://www.facebook.com/venusentertainment

title: 'Indian retail chains in Russia': Putin bats for expanding ties with New Delhi at BRICS Summit
description: Russian president Vladimir Putin spoke for the first time at the BRICS summit after invading Ukraine in February this year. China, which is chairing this year's brics summit, hosted leaders of Brazil, Russia, India and South Africa. Putin said at the summit that Russia has re-routed its trade with brics nations amid western sanctions. The U.S. led western bloc has slapped a slew of sanctions on Russia for its invasion of Ukraine. title: CGI 3D Animated Short: "Farewell / Slovo" - by Leon Vidmar and ZVVIKS | TheCGBros
description: TheCGBros Presents "Farewell / Slovo" - by Leon Vidmar and ZVVIKS  - Lovro is tired and sad. He fills the bathtub with water, looking at droplets dripping from the tap. As one hits the water surface, Lovro is reminded of the day he first went fishing with his grandpa. His thoughts take him to the fish pond, and the bathroom sounds and objects bring back memories of that day: putting a black worm on the hook, getting tangled in his grandpa's line, driving to the pond in a beaten old car, catching a fish for the first time and seeing it die. Memory and reality merge into one. title: Ekonomi Jerman Terancam Resesi setelah  Rusia Balas Sanksi Barat Hentikan Ekspor Gas ke Eropa
description: TRIBUN-VIDEO.COM - Operasi militer khusus Rusia ke Ukraina membuat Barat menjatuhkan sanksi terhadap Moskwa. |Termasuk Jerman yang ikut terlibat dalam pemberian sanksi tersebut. |Namun, justru ekonomi Jerman terancam mengalami resesi karena dibalas Rusia yang menghentikan ekspor energinya. |Dikutip dari Tribunnews.com, langkah kebijakan Presiden Putin yang memperketat aliran energi Rusia ke Eropa ternyata membawa dampak besar. |Rusia telah menghentikan ekspor gasnya ke sejumlah negara Uni Eropa dari Laut Baltik hingga Laut Adriatik.|Termasuk Jerman yang terkena imbasnya. |Terkini, ekonomi Jerman terancam babak belur. |Ancaman ini terjadi setelah perusahaan gas negara Rusia Gazprom memotong pasokan gasnya di pipa Nord Stream sebanyak tiga kali.|Resesi Jerman mulai tampak setelah Asosiasi Industri BDI Jerman memangkas perkiraan pertumbuhan ekonomi 2022.|Tercatat pertumbuhan ekonomi terganggu dari 3,5 persen menjadi 1,5 persen pada Selasa (21/6/2022). |â€œPenghentian pengiriman gas Rusia akan membuat Jerman mengalami resesi tak terhindarkan," jelas Asosiasi industri BDI.|Diungkapkan, kini pasokan gas Rusia ke Jerman hanya bekerja dengan kapasitas 40 persen.|Padahal permintaan minyak mengalami peningkatan. |Sementara itu, Menteri Ekonomi Jerman, Robert Habeck mengaku negaranya sangat bergantung pada pasokan gas Rusia. |Kendati begitu, Jerman akan memulai beralih ke penggunaan batu bara pada akhir Juni nanti. |Hal ini sebagai langkah untuk mengurangi ketergantungan minyak dan gas Rusia. |Dengan kebijakan ini, Menteri Ekonomi optimis dapat membantu Jerman menghemat stok gasnya.|(Tribun-Video.com/ Tribunnews.com)|Video Editor: Dyah Ayu Ambarwati|Host: Bima Maulana|Artikel ini telah tayang di Tribunnews.com dengan judul Ekonomi Jerman Menuju Jurang Resesi oleh Embargo Gas Rusia, https://www.tribunnews.com/bisnis/2022/06/22/ekonomi-jerman-menuju-jurang-resesi-oleh-embargo-gas-rusia.|Penulis: Namira Yunia Lestanti|Editor: Choirul Arifin

title: Stanley Cup Final Game 4: Colorado Avalanche vs. Tampa Bay Lightning | Full Game Highlights

title: Ganjar Ungkit Perintah Megawati Saat Ditanya Salam Komando Dengan Bambang Pacul
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV  Salam komando antara Gubernur Jawa Tengah Ganjar Pranowo dengan Bambang Wuryanto menyedot perhatian publik. ||||Pasalnya hubungan keduanya sempat dikabarkan memanas karena ketidakhadiran Ganjar di acara PDIP di Jawa Tengah. ||||Ganjar pun mengungkap keterkaitan salam komando dengan kekompakan menjalankan perintah Ketua Umum PDIP Megawati Soekarnoputri.||||Baca Juga Momen Ganjar dan Bambang Pacul Salam Komando Disorak Para Kader di Acara Rakernas di https://www.kompas.tv/article/301133/momen-ganjar-dan-bambang-pacul-salam-komando-disorak-para-kader-di-acara-rakernas||||"Salam komando ya kita tunjukkan ini kan rakernas nih. Kita mesti kompak dari perintah Ketum, targetnya ya kita semua mesti bekerja, sesimpel itu saja dan semua tersenyum, dan mendapatkan respons dari Indonesia, wah rakernasnya kompak, rakernasnya ini,"ujar Ganjar, Rabu (22/6/2022). ||||Ganjar pun menilai pertemanannya dengan Bambang Wuryanto seperti junior ke senior.||||"Itu biasalah, namanya juga seperti ramalan cuaca, kadang hujan kadang panas. Mas Pacul itu di UGM, temen saya, senior saya, dulu bareng di Kesekjenan bareng saya, di Badiklat bareng saya, di fraksi bareng saya, jadi biasa saja buat saya," ujarnya.||||Video Editor: Arief || ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/301927/ganjar-ungkit-perintah-megawati-saat-ditanya-salam-komando-dengan-bambang-pacul

title: Partai Mana Saja Yang Akan Berkoalisi Dengan NasDem | Satu Meja The Forum (3)
description: KOMPASTV - Partai Nasdem sudah memutuskan tiga nama akan diusung pada pilpres 2024 mendatang. Meski demikian hingga saat ini Partai Nasdem masih memilih sendiri, tak kunjung memutuskan dengan siapa akan berkoalisi.||||Gubernur Jawa Tengah, Ganjar Pranowo menjadi salah satu dari tiga nama yang ditetapkan. Akankah Ganjar menjadi jembatan koalisi antara Partai Nasdem dengan PDI Perjuangan? Atau sebaliknya, berubah menjadi oposisi?||||Lalu seperti apa jurus politik Surya Paloh dalam menentukan koalisi? ||||Ketua Umum Partai NasDem, Surya Paloh, mengutarakan kesamaan ideologi dan kesamaan memilih calon presiden, akan menjadi syarat Partai NasDem untuk berkoalisi dengan partai lain. ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/301973/partai-mana-saja-yang-akan-berkoalisi-dengan-nasdem-satu-meja-the-forum-3

description: Tonton tayangan lengkap Indosiar di vidio.com atau klik https://www.vidio.com/live/7642 |Halo Sahabat Vidio, kembali lagi di Poles - Kepoin Lesti. Siapa disini yang ingin bulan madu bersama sang kekasih nih?? Hemmmm apalagi kalau bulan madunya ke Eropa, pasti sangat didamba-dambakan juga kan Sahabat Vidio? Kalau Lesti Kejora bulan madu kemaren tidak mengajak Baby L Sahabat Vidio, karena banyak pertimbangan juga yang menyebabkan Baby L tidak ikut liburan bersama papap dan bunda. Tapi disamping itu, Baby L pun juga healing loh Sahabat Vidio. Baby L bersama enin juga liburan ke Bandung, yang membuat Lesti Kejora dan Rizky Billar pun iri kepada enin dan team yang ke Bandung. Duhhh jadi gimana sih ini, enakan ke Eropa atau ke Bandung yah?? Yaudah deh daripada penasaran seperti apa cerita Lesti Kejora selama bulan madu di Eropa dan cerita Baby L di Bandung seperti apa? title: Devastating earthquake in Afghanistan compounds humanitarian crisis
description: The Taliban leaders of Afghanistan are appealing for outside help after a devastating earthquake killed at least 1,000 people Wednesday and injured another 1,500. The quake struck in the eastern mountains near the Pakistan border. Officials warned the death toll may still rise as search efforts continue. Samira Sayed-Rahman, of the International Rescue Committee, joins Amna Nawaz to discuss.|Stream your PBS favorites with the PBS app: https://to.pbs.org/2Jb8twG|Find more from PBS NewsHour at https://www.pbs.org/newshour|Subscribe to our YouTube channel: https://bit.ly/2HfsCD6|Follow us:|TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@pbsnews|Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/newshour|Instagram: http://www.instagram.com/newshour|Facebook: http://www.pbs.org/newshour|Subscribe:|PBS NewsHour podcasts: https://www.pbs.org/newshour/podcasts|Newsletters: https://www.pbs.org/newshour/subscribe

title: Devastating earthquake kills more than 1,000 people in Afghanistan - BBC News
description: A powerful earthquake has killed at least 1,000 people and injured 1,500 in eastern Afghanistan.|The country's Taliban government appealed for international help for the rescue effort in the province of Paktika.|Hundreds of houses were destroyed. It is the deadliest earthquake to strike Afghanistan in two decades and a major challenge for the Taliban, the Islamist movement which regained power last year after the Western-backed government collapsed.|The earthquake struck about 44km from the city of Khost and tremors were felt as far away as Pakistan and India. |Huw Edwards presents BBC News at Ten reporting by Secunder Kermani in Afghanistan and world affairs correspondent Caroline Hawley.|Please subscribe HERE http://bit.ly/1rbfUog|#BBCNews

title: 50 Bangkai Hewan Ternak Diduga Akibat PMK Ditemukan di Aliran Sungai Serang
description: KABUPATEN SEMARANG, KOMPAS.TV -  Warga Desa Susukan, Kabupaten Semarang Jawa Tengah menemukan sekitar 50 bangkai kambing, di aliran Sungai Serang.||||Diduga bangkai kambing dari peternakan di luar Desa Susukan, karena mempunyai tanda khusus berupa kalung yang terpasang di leher.||||Menurut saksi mata, pada Senin (20/06) malam ada sebuah truk parkir di Jembatan Sungai Serang yang diduga membuang bangkai.||||Baca Juga Kebakaran di Pondok Permata Sekumpul Martapura, Lurah Upayakan Korban dapat Bantuan di https://www.kompas.tv/article/301913/kebakaran-di-pondok-permata-sekumpul-martapura-lurah-upayakan-korban-dapat-bantuan||||Dari hasil penyelidikan sementara, polisi mendapati saksi yang diminta membantu membuang puluhan bangkai kambing dengan imbalan Rp 100 ribu.||||Puluhan bangkai kambing dikirim dari Sumatera menggunakan 2 truk.||||Dari ciri fisik, dinas terkait memastikan bangkai kambing terjangkit penyakit mulut dan kuku (PMK).||||Penyidik dalri Polres Semarang menyebut total ada 97 bangkai hewan ternak yang dibuang di aliran Sungai Serang, Kabupaten Semarang.||||Baca Juga AFC Cup 2022 Zona ASEAN Mulai 24 Juni: Format & Sistem Kompetisi, Bagaimana Peluang Wakil Indonesia? di https://www.kompas.tv/article/301916/afc-cup-2022-zona-asean-mulai-24-juni-format-sistem-kompetisi-bagaimana-peluang-wakil-indonesia||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/301923/50-bangkai-hewan-ternak-diduga-akibat-pmk-ditemukan-di-aliran-sungai-serang

title: BOAI Episode 9: Final Framing and Two Additional Projects!
description: In this episode of Building on an Island, Wade visits two other worksites on Block island before we head to the BOAI site. At the first home, Wade and his team are installing a slate roof. He shares why they chose slate over other roofing materials, and why slate tile roofs are called a "forever roof." On the second site, a gorgeous Queen Anne renovation, Wade discusses how they're going to restore this 160-year-old home while maintaining its historical and architectural integrity. The house had a lot of rot in the original wood, so the team replaced much of the framing and created a floor system where none originally existed. They'll also have to replace all of the windows and doors. At the Building on an Island home, Wade discusses supply chain and other issues that the team is navigating. The crew has finished miscellaneous framing in the basement, living room, and kitchen. The exterior team has been working on the balcony and the white, PVC Versatex trim, and other details, including deck boards and asphalt shingles on the roof. He even shares his roofer's method of preventing hurricane-force winds from tearing away the shingles. As the exposure limit for the Huber ZIP system approaches, Wade gets advice on how to continue without voiding the warranty so they can install shakes and a stone veneer.|Subscribe and follow my Podcast on Apple or Spotify!|Apple: https://apple.co/32AOwgU|Spotify: https://spoti.fi/3FXNg4X|Sign up for our twice-weekly newsletter:|https://buildshownetwork.com/newsletter|To sponsor a video or advertise with us visit:|https://www.buildproductions.com|Want to learn more about building? https://buildshownetwork.com/|Build Show Network on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/thebuildshow/|Huge thanks to our Show sponsors Builders FirstSource, Polywall, Huber, Rockwool & Viewrail for helping to make these videos possible! These are all trusted companies that Matt has worked with for years and trusts their products in the homes he builds. title: Presiden Jokowi Membuka Kongres Nasional XXXII dan Sidang MPA XXXI PMKRI, Samarinda, 22 Juni 2022
description: *Buka Kongres Nasional ke-32 PMKRI, Presiden Pastikan IKN Pindah Sesuai Rencana*|Presiden Joko Widodo memastikan bahwa pemindahan ibu kota negara Republik Indonesia dari Jakarta ke Ibu Kota Nusantara (IKN) akan tetap dilakukan sesuai dengan rencana yang telah ditetapkan oleh pemerintah dan undang-undang. Menurut Presiden, pemindahan ibu kota negara merupakan gagasan lama dari sejumlah pemimpin Indonesia terdahulu yang belum direalisasikan hingga saat ini.|"Ini adalah sebuah mimpi lama, gagasan lama yang belum dieksekusi, dan sekarang telah kita eksekusi dan ada _back up_ undang-undangnya yaitu Undang-Undang Ibu Kota Negara," ujar Presiden dalam sambutannya saat membuka secara resmi Kongres Nasional XXXII dan Sidang Majelis Permusyawaratan Anggota XXXI Perhimpunan Mahasiswa Katolik Republik Indonesia (PMKRI) yang digelar di Samarinda Convention Hall, Kota Samarinda, pada Rabu, 22 Juni 2022.|Dalam kesempatan tersebut, Presiden memaparkan sejumlah alasan mengenai pentingnya pemindahan ibu kota negara. Salah satunya adalah pemerataan ekonomi yang ingin diwujudkan di seluruh penjuru Tanah Air dan tidak terpusat di satu pulau yang ada di Indonesia. |"Yang paling penting memang kita ingin Indonesiasentris bukan Jawasentris. Kita garis dari barat ke timur, dari utara ke selatan, ketemu di paling tengah itu yaitu Provinsi Kalimantan Timur," ungkap Presiden.|Selain itu, Presiden juga menjelaskan bahwa perpindahan ibu kota tidak hanya melakukan pemindahan secara fisik sejumlah infrastruktur yang ada di Jakarta. Menurut Presiden, perubahan pola pikir, birokrasi, dan cara kerja baru yang menggunakan teknologi akan menjadi prioritas pemerintah di IKN.|"Di sini lah akan kita mulai _future economy_, _green economy_, _future technology_, _future knowledge_ semuanya memang ingin kita lakukan di sini. Rumah sakit ya rumah sakit internasional, universitas ya universitas yang kelasnya betul-betul internasional dan kita harapkan ini juga bisa membuka yang namanya _future job_ dan _future skill_," ucap Presiden. |Presiden pun berharap IKN dapat menjadi magnet bagi talenta-talenta dalam negeri maupun luar negeri. Presiden mengatakan bahwa nantinya IKN akan memiliki desain dan fasilitas yang mendukung konsep _ten minutes city_, 70 persen area hijau, 80 persen transportasi publik ramah lingkungan, hingga penggunaan energi hijau.|"Ini desain-desain kota masa depan yang saya kira ini adalah miliknya anak-anak muda," tutur Presiden.|Turut mendampingi Presiden dalam kegiatan tersebut adalah Ketua DPR RI Puan Maharani, Menteri Sekretaris Negara Pratikno, Menteri Investasi/Kepala BKPM Bahlil Lahadalia, Menteri Pemuda dan Olahraga Zainudin Amali, Gubernur Kalimantan Timur Isran Noor, Wali Kota Samarinda Andi Harun, dan Ketua Presidium PMKRI Benidiktus Papa.|Samarinda, 22 Juni 2022|Biro Pers, Media, dan Informasi Sekretariat Presiden|Website: https://www.presidenri.go.id|YouTube: Sekretariat Presiden

Central to that journey is one of the significant and influential people in Elvisâ€™s life, Priscilla Presley (Olivia DeJonge). |Starring alongside Butler and Hanks, award-winning theatre actress Helen Thomson (â€œTop of the Lake: China Girl,â€ â€œRakeâ€) plays Elvisâ€™s mother, Gladys, Richard Roxburgh (â€œMoulin Rouge!â€ â€œBreath,â€ â€œHacksaw Ridgeâ€) portrays Elvisâ€™s father, Vernon, and DeJonge (â€œThe Visit,â€ â€œStray Dollsâ€) plays Priscilla. Luke Bracey (â€œHacksaw Ridge,â€ â€œPoint Breakâ€) plays Jerry Schilling, Natasha Bassett (â€œHail, Caesar!â€) plays Dixie Locke, David Wenham (â€œThe Lord of the Ringsâ€ Trilogy, â€œLion,â€ â€œ300â€) plays Hank Snow, Kelvin Harrison Jr. (â€œThe Trial of the Chicago 7,â€ â€œThe High Noteâ€) plays B.B. King, Xavier Samuel (â€œAdore,â€ â€œLove & Friendship,â€ â€œThe Twilight Saga: Eclipseâ€) plays Scotty Moore, and Kodi Smit-McPhee (â€œThe Power of the Dogâ€) plays Jimmie Rodgers Snow. |Also in the cast, Dacre Montgomery (â€œStranger Things,â€ â€œThe Broken Heart Galleryâ€) plays TV director Steve Binder, alongside Australian actors Leon Ford (â€œGallipoli,â€ â€œThe Pacificâ€) as Tom Diskin, Kate Mulvany (â€œThe Great Gatsby,â€ â€œHuntersâ€) as Marion Keisker, Gareth Davies (â€œPeter Rabbit,â€ â€œHuntersâ€) as Bones Howe, Charles Grounds (â€œCrazy Rich Asians,â€ â€œCampâ€) as Billy Smith, Josh McConville (â€œFantasy Islandâ€) as Sam Phillips, and Adam Dunn (â€œHome and Awayâ€) as Bill Black. |To play additional iconic musical artists in the film, Luhrmann cast singer/songwriter Yola as Sister Rosetta Tharpe, model Alton Mason as Little Richard, Austin, Texas native Gary Clark Jr. as Arthur Crudup, and artist Shonka Dukureh as Willie Mae â€œBig Mamaâ€ Thornton. |Oscar nominee Luhrmann (â€œThe Great Gatsby,â€ â€œMoulin Rouge!â€) directed from a screenplay by Baz Luhrmann & Sam Bromell and Baz Luhrmann & Craig Pearce and Jeremy Doner, story by Baz Luhrmann and Jeremy Doner. The filmâ€™s producers are Luhrmann, Oscar winner Catherine Martin (â€œThe Great Gatsby,â€ â€œMoulin Rouge!â€), Gail Berman, Patrick McCormick and Schuyler Weiss. Toby Emmerich, Courtenay Valenti and Kevin McCormick executive produced. |The directorâ€™s behind-the-scenes creative team includes director of photography Mandy Walker (â€œMulan,â€ â€œAustraliaâ€), Oscar-winning production designer and costume designer Catherine Martin (â€œThe Great Gatsby,â€ â€œMoulin Rouge!â€), production designer Karen Murphy (â€œA Star Is Bornâ€), editors Matt Villa (â€œThe Great Gatsby,â€ â€œAustraliaâ€) and Jonathan Redmond (â€œThe Great Gatsbyâ€), Oscar-nominated visual effects supervisor Thomas Wood (â€œMad Max: Fury Roadâ€), music supervisor Anton Monsted (â€œAustralia,â€ â€œMoulin Rouge!â€) and composer Elliott Wheeler (â€œThe Get Downâ€). |Principal photography on â€œElvisâ€ took place in Queensland, Australia with the support of the Queensland Government, Screen Queensland, and the Australian Governmentâ€™s Producer Offset program. |A Warner Bros. Pictures Presentation, A Bazmark Production, A Jackal Group Production, A Baz Luhrmann Film, â€œElvisâ€ will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures. It is set to release in theaters in North America on June 24, 2022, and internationally beginning 22 June 2022.

title: Sonic Origins Review
description: Sonic is back! This time, members of the Sonic Mania team have updated Sonic for 16:9 with Sonic Origins, a Sonic compilation featuring Sonic 1, Sonic 2, Sonic CD, and Sonic 3 & Knuckles. While Sonic Origins isn't the first time we've seen a compilation, it's the first time we've seen Sonic remade from the ground up with an updated aspect ratio. Sonic Origins releases June 23, 2022.

title: IT'S HERE! My Brand New Zenvo TSR-S in the UK | ROAD TO ZENVO Part 9
description: The day has finally arrived to reveal my brand new Zenvo TSR-S in all its glory! After a Shmeemobile convoy to the Goodwood Festival of Speed, my ultimate MEGACAR is presented on the Zenvo stand. It's quite literally a dream come true, what a bonkers machine it is!|This moment is truly special, heading to Goodwood for the Festival of Speed with a number of my cars ahead of seeing the completed TSR-S for the very first time, at such an iconic venue. We've seen it along the way, but now it's here to reveal to everyone!|The Road to Zenvo series has covered the process behind the TSR-S, from initial ideas and specification, through manufacturing and assembly, to now presenting the car itself at one of the most incredible car events in the world. I've been visiting the Goodwood Festival of Speed for over a decade, devoting huge time to the Supercar Paddock, and now the totally surreal experience of my very own car being right here.|The day begins, setting off from @The Shmuseum with my Ford GT, joined by the AMG GT Black Series, Vantage GT8 and C63 Black Series, plus @Vehicle Virgins and @Zachs Garage, while the Senna is transported down to be on the @BOTB stand. It's a beautiful day, and could not be better for such a special outing, and the delivery of my most extreme, most powerful, and most ludicrous Shmeemobile ever.|We've launched our new purple Shmee150 Future Wear carbon fibre sunglasses, with a limited edition of only 75 pairs available, you can get them here: https://www.future-wear.com/products/shmee150-full-carbon-fibre-lilla-perlemor-polarized-shades-limited-run-only-75-pairs|Thanks for watching, Tim|Chapters:|00:00 Intro|01:09 Delivery Plans|02:33 Load Out|03:36 Convoy to Goodwood Begins|05:18 Senna Incident|06:18 New Purple Sunglasses|06:55 Tunnel Run|08:21 Journey Continues|10:08 Arrival at Goodwood FOS|10:55 Zenvo TSR-S Reveal|15:02 Engine Bay|19:34 Additonal Details|21:04 Wrap Up|#Zenvo #TSRS #NewCar||||Subscribe: http://bit.ly/Shmee150YT||Website: http://www.shmee150.com||Shop: http://shop.shmee150.com||Instagram: http://www.instagram.com/shmee150||Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/shmee150

title: Obi-Wan Kenobi Ending Explained
description: HELLO THERE!|So, the Obi-Wan Kenobi series has drawn to a close and we have to say it ended in quite the fashion, with an epic lightsaber duel, some cool cameos and a return of a line we have been waiting so long for. It is all quite a satisfying conclusion, and although there are certainly some continuity quibbles and potential plot holes created by the series, it all sets up A New Hope and the classic Star Wars saga pretty nicely. |But what does this all mean? How does it play out into A New Hope? What did that final shot and line mean? And will there be a second season? These are the questions we seek to answer in this video, as will go through the final episode with a fine comb and hopefully provide the answers to any other questions you might have. We will look at the references to A New Hope, the importance of that particular showdown and the ambiguous fate of one of the showâ€™s new characters. We will also discuss what a potential second season might look like, who could return, whether or not we will see the Skywalker twins again, who the primary antagonist could be and the possibility of the return of another familiar face. We will also use evidence from the people who worked on the show to see whether or not a second season might happen, and why there are some exciting possibilities for Obi-Wan moving forward. But before we do that, letâ€™s go over the ending once more.|What did you make of this video? Were you a fan of the series? What did you make of the ending? Do you want a second season? If so, what would you like to see? Let us know in the comments below and make sure to subscribe to the channel today for all this and more.|GOODBYE THERE!|Subscribe: http://bit.ly/Subscribe-to-Screenrant|Chapters:|0:00 Intro |0:30 Ending Explained|4:36 Season 2|Check out Screen Rantâ€™s official TikTok! |https://www.tiktok.com/@screenrant |Our Social Media:|https://twitter.com/screenrant |https://www.facebook.com/ScreenRant  |https://www.linkedin.com/company/screen-rant/ |Our Website:|http://screenrant.com/|Written by: Aiden M|Narrated by: Justin Freitas @JustinFreitasVO|Edited by: Gullivar Du Katt|For copyright matters please contact us at: legal@valnetinc.com

King, Xavier Samuel (â€œAdore,â€ â€œLove & Friendship,â€ â€œThe Twilight Saga: Eclipseâ€) plays Scotty Moore, and Kodi Smit-McPhee (â€œThe Power of the Dogâ€) plays Jimmie Rodgers Snow. |Also in the cast, Dacre Montgomery (â€œStranger Things,â€ â€œThe Broken Heart Galleryâ€) plays TV director Steve Binder, alongside Australian actors Leon Ford (â€œGallipoli,â€ â€œThe Pacificâ€) as Tom Diskin, Kate Mulvany (â€œThe Great Gatsby,â€ â€œHuntersâ€) as Marion Keisker, Gareth Davies (â€œPeter Rabbit,â€ â€œHuntersâ€) as Bones Howe, Charles Grounds (â€œCrazy Rich Asians,â€ â€œCampâ€) as Billy Smith, Josh McConville (â€œFantasy Islandâ€) as Sam Phillips, and Adam Dunn (â€œHome and Awayâ€) as Bill Black. |To play additional iconic musical artists in the film, Luhrmann cast singer/songwriter Yola as Sister Rosetta Tharpe, model Alton Mason as Little Richard, Austin, Texas native Gary Clark Jr. as Arthur Crudup, and artist Shonka Dukureh as Willie Mae â€œBig Mamaâ€ Thornton. |Oscar nominee Luhrmann (â€œThe Great Gatsby,â€ â€œMoulin Rouge!â€) directed from a screenplay by Baz Luhrmann & Sam Bromell and Baz Luhrmann & Craig Pearce and Jeremy Doner, story by Baz Luhrmann and Jeremy Doner. title: Reggie Miller getting his night ruined needs a deep rewind | 2004 ECF Pacers-Pistons
description: Poor Reggie Miller. Or alternatively, depending on your fandom, take that Reggie Miller! The guy was 38, running out of chances to win a title, and this night did not go his way. But there's so much more going on in this series.|We've got Rick Carlisle coaching the Pacers, against a Piston's team that fired him a year prior.  We've got a classic Reggie Miller three pointer to win game one.  We've got Rasheed Wallace guaranteeing a game two win for the Pistons. And we've got the surprise ending of this game...should I say it or leave it for the video? If you've read this far, you probably know what happened. And, I mean, it's from 2004... I can't hold back I'm gonna say it: We've got one of the best chase down blocks in NBA history from Tayshaun Prince.  Sorry if I spoiled the video. title: Penggantian Nama Jalan oleh Pemprov DKI Ditolak Warga
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Penggantian nama jalan oleh Pemprov DKI Jakarta mendapat penolakan.||||Puluhan warga di Kebon Jeruk, Jakarta Barat menolak karena penggantian nama jalan tanpa sosialisasi.||||Baca Juga Momen Anies dan Ketua DPRD Manortor dalam Paripurna HUT DKI Jakarta ke-495 di https://www.kompas.tv/article/301633/momen-anies-dan-ketua-dprd-manortor-dalam-paripurna-hut-dki-jakarta-ke-495||||Spanduk bertuliskan penolakan pergantian nama jalan dibentangkan oleh warga Jalan Madrasah II, Sukabumi Utara, Jakarta Barat.||||Warga kecewa, kebijakan dianggap sepihak tanpa melibatkan warga dalam musyawarah.||||Warga dari 3 rukun warga menolak pergantian nama jalan. Madrasah II menjadi Syekh Abdul Karim bin Asfan.||||Selain tak ada sosialisasi, warga juga kawatir dengan masalah pengurusan administrasi domisili dan surat menyurat.||||Bahkan belum diresmikan, plang nama sudah dipasang.||||Sebelumnya, dalam menyambut hari ulang tahun DKI Jakarta ke-495, ada sekitar 22 jalan, serta 5 perkampungan yang diganti namanya.||||Pemprov DKI menyatakan, penggantian nama jalan dengan nama-nama tokoh Betawi untuk mengenang jasa para pendahulu khususnya masyarakat Betawi.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/301860/penggantian-nama-jalan-oleh-pemprov-dki-ditolak-warga

title: Elektabilitasnya Masih Tinggi, Ganjar Pranowo Akan Diusung Maju Capres oleh PDIP?
description: KOMPAS.TV - Survei Litbang Kompas, tiga nama tokoh potensial capres 2024 kembali ditempati Prabowo Subianto, Ganjar Pranowo, dan Anies Baswedan. Ketiganya masih menempati posisi tiga teratas.||||Baca Juga Terungkap, Ini Profesi Ganjar setelah Tak Jadi Gubernur: Seenggaknya YouTuber, Bisa Lumayanlah di https://www.kompas.tv/article/301849/terungkap-ini-profesi-ganjar-setelah-tak-jadi-gubernur-seenggaknya-youtuber-bisa-lumayanlah||||Dalam survei yang dilakukan 26 Mei hingga 4 Juni, Prabowo Subianto di posisi teratas dengan 25,3 persen, Ganjar Pranowo 22 persen, dan Anies Baswedan 12,6 persen.||||Menjelang Pilpres 2024, nama Ganjar disebut-sebut sebagai calon presiden potensial di Pilpres 2024.||||Bahkan, Partai Nasdem mengusulkan nama Ganjar Pranowo menjadi bakal calon presiden untuk Pilpres 2024.||||Dalam Rakernas PDIP di hadapan Ganjar, Megawati mengingatkan bahwa kader PDIP tidak boleh bermain dua kaki.||||Sementara itu, nama Ganjar masih di posisi dua besar bahkan ada kenaikan sebagai tokoh potensial capres 20204. Lalu akankah Ganjar diusung maju pilpres? Simak dialog selengkapnya berikut ini.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/301889/elektabilitasnya-masih-tinggi-ganjar-pranowo-akan-diusung-maju-capres-oleh-pdip

title: Karnataka MLA slaps, abuses Principal of Govt ITI College; Netizens fume, demand lawmaker's arrest
description: A video of Mandya JD(S) MLA M Srinivas purportedly slapping the principal of an ITI has gone viral on social media. The incident is said to have occurred during the inauguration of the renovated Nalwadi Krishnaraja Wadiyar ITI College in Mandya district on Monday.  The video in which the exchange between the legislator and the principal is not clear shows that as soon as the principal appears before him, Srinivas abuses him verbally and slaps him twice, in front of other people and the staff. title: The Office x Minions
description: Minions: The Rise of Gru | Only in Theaters July 1st. |- -|Follow #Illumination and #Minions:|https://www.instagram.com/illuminatio...|https://www.facebook.com/illuminationent|https://twitter.com/illumination|https://www.instagram.com/minions|https://www.tiktok.com/@minions|https://www.facebook.com/minions|https://twitter.com/minions|This summer, from the biggest global animated franchise in history, comes the origin story of how the worldâ€™s greatest supervillain first met his iconic Minions, forged cinemaâ€™s most despicable crew and faced off against the most unstoppable criminal force ever assembled in Minions: The Rise of Gru.| |Long before he becomes the master of evil, Gru (OscarÂ® nominee Steve Carell) is just a 12-year-old boy in 1970s suburbia, plotting to take over the world from his basement. |Itâ€™s not going particularly well. When Gru crosses paths with the Minions, including Kevin, Stuart, Bob, and Ottoâ€”a new Minion sporting braces and a desperate need to pleaseâ€”this unexpected family joins forces. Together, they build their first lair, design their first weapons, and strive to execute their first missions.| |When the infamous supervillain supergroup, the Vicious 6, oust their leaderâ€”legendary martial arts fighter Wild Knuckles (OscarÂ® winner Alan Arkin)â€” Gru, their most devoted fanboy, interviews to become their newest member. The Vicious 6 is not impressed by the diminutive, wannabe villain, but then Gru outsmarts (and enrages) them, and he suddenly finds himself the mortal enemy of the apex of evil. With Gru on the run, the Minions attempt to master the art of kung fu to help save him, and Gru discovers that even bad guys need a little help from their friends. | |Featuring more spectacular action than any film in Illumination history and packed with the franchiseâ€™s signature subversive humor, Minions: The Rise of Gru stars a thrilling new cast, including, the Vicious 6: Taraji P. Henson as cool and confident leader Belle Bottom, whose chain belt doubles as a lethal disco-ball mace; Jean-Claude Van Damme as the nihilistic Jean Clawed, whoâ€™s armed (literally) with a giant robotic claw; Lucy Lawless as Nunchuck, whose traditional nunâ€™s habit hides her deadly nun-chucks; Dolph Lundgren as Swedish roller-skate champion Svengeance, who dispenses his enemies with spin kicks from his spiked skates; and Danny Trejo as Stronghold, whose giant iron hands are both a menace to others and a burden to him. | |The film also stars Russell Brand as Young Dr. Nefario, an aspiring mad scientist, Michelle Yeoh as Master Chow, an acupuncturist with mad kung fu skills, and OscarÂ® winner Julie Andrews as Gruâ€™s maddeningly self-absorbed mom.| |Steered by the franchiseâ€™s original creators, Minions: The Rise of Gru is produced by visionary Illumination founder and CEO Chris Meledandri and his longtime collaborators Janet Healy and Chris Renaud. The film is directed by returning franchise filmmaker Kyle Balda (Despicable Me 3, Minions), co-directed by Brad Ableson (The Simpsons) and Jonathan del Val (The Secret Life of Pets films), and features the iconic voice of Pierre Coffin as the Minions and a killer â€™70s soundtrack courtesy of legendary Grammy-winning music producer Jack Antonoff.

title: DreadOut 2 - Announce Trailer | PS5 & PS4 Games
description: DreadOut 2 is a third-person horror adventure that draws inspiration from Indonesian folklore and urban legend. Play as Linda Meillinda, a high school student with a supernatural power â€“ the ability to sense and see ghosts. With the aid of her trusty smartphone, Linda must hunt the nightmarish spirits and dark forces that threaten not only her hometown, but all of mankind.|This spine-chilling sequel expands on the cult hit original with all-new melee combat and a greater emphasis on exploration, making DreadOut 2 another compelling and terrifying addition to the horror genre.|Features|â€¢ Banish them all! Hunt and defeat intangible ghosts with Lindaâ€™s smartphone camera, or use melee weapons and projectiles against physical ghosts|â€¢ A world of dread: Explore Lindaâ€™s hometown and beyond, talk to residents (alive and dead!), complete side-quests, and delve deeper into DreadOut lore|â€¢ Discover ghosts and urban legends: Search out spirits and uncover local myths to complete the Ghostpedia app on Lindaâ€™s smartphone|â€¢ Terrifying boss spirits: Keep your nerve as you battle the supernatural realmâ€™s most hostile ghosts, including the chilling Kuntilanak, and horrifying Gore Surgeon|#ps5games #ps4games |Rated Mature

title: Lyle, Lyle, Crocodile - Official Teaser Trailer (2022) Shawn Mendes, Javier Bardem
description: Check out the teaser trailer for Lyle, Lyle, Crocodile, the upcoming comedy musical featuring Shawn Mendes as a singing crocodile.||||When the Primm family moves to New York City, their son Josh struggles to adapt to his new school and friends. However, all of that changes when he meets a singing crocodile called Lyle living in the attic. The two quickly become friends, but when Lyle's existence is threatened by evil neighbor Mr. Grumps, the Primm's must work together with Lyle's charismatic owner, Hector P. Valenti.||||Based on the best-selling book series by Bernard Waber, Lyle, Lyle, Crocodile stars Constance Wu, Scoot McNairy, Javier Bardem, Winslow Fegley, Brett Gelman. It'll also feature original songs performed by Shawn Mendes and written by the songwriting team behind The Greatest Showman.||||Lyle, Lyle, Crocodile opens in US theaters on October 7, 2022.|#IGN #Movies #LyleLyleCrocodile

title: Is Sri Lanka a victim of Chinese 'debt traps'? - BBC Newsnight
description: Sri Lanka's economic crisis continues to run out of control and the country is requesting an emergency bailout from the International Monetary Fund. |However, the major debts the country has racked up in borrowing from China are standing in the way of a bailout being agreed. |Please subscribe HERE http://bit.ly/1rbfUog|Chinese money has flooded into many developing countries over the past few years but some claim that these loans are designed as 'debt traps'.|It's claimed that if a country can't repay then China is entitled to seize critical infrastructure such as ports and thereby strengthen it's global influence. |Others suggest that China is not in fact exploiting developing nations but their investment may facilitate more local level corruption. |Newsnight's economics editor Ben Chu went to Sri Lanka to investigate the impact of Chinese money and what implications this may have for the global cost of living crisis. |The film was produced by Scarlett Barter and filmed/ edited by Jack Garland. Production support was provided by Zaufaran Mohamed.|Newsnight is the BBC's flagship news and current affairs TV programme - with analysis, debate, exclusives, and robust interviews. |Website: https://www.bbc.co.uk/newsnight |Twitter: https://twitter.com/BBCNewsnight |Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/bbcnewsnight.|#BBCNews
tags: bbc|bbc news|news

title: Powerful earthquake kills hundreds in Afghanistan - BBC News
description: A powerful earthquake has killed at least 920 people and left hundreds more injured in Afghanistan, Taliban officials have said.|Pictures show landslides and ruined mud-built homes in eastern Paktika province, where rescuers have been scrambling to treat the injured.|In remote areas, helicopters have been ferrying victims to hospitals.|Taliban leader Hibatullah Akhundzada said hundreds of houses were destroyed and the death toll was likely to rise.|Please subscribe HERE http://bit.ly/1rbfUog|#BBCNews

title: [Full] Pernyataan Lengkap Surya Paloh dan Presiden PKS di DPP Nasdem
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV  Presiden PKS Ahmad Syaikhu bertandang ke kantor DPP Partai Nasdem di Jakarta pada 22 Juni 2022.||||Presiden PKS Ahmad Syaikhu bertemu dengan Ketum Partai Nasdem Surya Paloh.||||Usai pertemuan, Surya Paloh mengatakan belum ada satu hal yang cukup serius menjadi pembahasan keduanya.||||Baca Juga Sinyal Koalisi Nasdem-PKS Mulai Kencang, Surya Paloh Sebut Sudah Ada Modal Awal untuk Bersama di https://www.kompas.tv/article/301725/sinyal-koalisi-nasdem-pks-mulai-kencang-surya-paloh-sebut-sudah-ada-modal-awal-untuk-bersama||||"Bagi kami berdua belum ada satu hal yang cukup serius menjadi pembahasan di antara kami, tetapi telah mendapatkan sesuatu yang dimaknai," kata Surya pada wartawan. Baca juga: Presiden PKS Ahmad Syaikhu Temui Surya Paloh di Nasdem Tower Namun, ia mengaku Partai Nasdem memiliki banyak kesamaan pandangan dengan PKS terkait persiapan Pemilu 2024.||||Hal itu menjadi faktor yang memungkinkan terjalinnya kerja sama antara dua partai politik (parpol) tersebut.||||"Ada banyak kesamaan pandangan, pikiran, yang amat sangat dimungkinkan untuk dikolaborasikan bersama menjadi suatu harapan bagi meningkatkan upaya-upaya yang memang harus dipersiapkan dari dini agar kualitas Pemilu 2024 bisa jauh lebih baik," papar dia.||||Video Editor: Vila Randita||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/301749/full-pernyataan-lengkap-surya-paloh-dan-presiden-pks-di-dpp-nasdem

title: Western sanctions start to bite in Russia's aviation sector | DW Business
description: The Russian invasion of Ukraine has slowed the post pandemic recovery of the industry on a global level.
